  <h2>More About the Author</h2>

      <div class="author_page_link content">
        <span class="carat">&rsaquo;</span> 
        <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Mason-Currey/e/B0093C1JK6">
          Visit Amazon's Mason Currey Page
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="content" style="float:left;width:100px;">
        <div class="authorImageSingle">
          <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Mason-Currey/e/B0093C1JK6">
            







      <div id="authorMainImageBlock" class="authorImageBlock">
         <img src="http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41gpkSguX4L._SX80_.jpg" width="80" alt="Mason Currey" id="B0093C1JK6" height="112" border="0" />
      </div>

          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    <div class="mainContent">
      
  
      Mason Currey was born in Honesdale, Pennsylvania, and graduated from the University of North Carolina at Asheville. His writing has appeared in Slate, Print, and Metropolis, where he was an editor for six years. He lives in Los Angeles.


